Avacaster,is,a,webcasting,and,webconferencing,solution,The,Avacaster,API,is,a,RESTful,or,SOAP,based,API,that,lets,users,manage,and,edit,their,events,on,their,Avacaster,server,Users,can,create,or,duplicate,events,get,the,status,of,the,event,add,users,to,the,event,and,create,polls,quizzes,and,archives,Authentication,requires,a,username,and,password,for,every,call,and,data,is,returned,in,an,XML,or,JSON,format